WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.349 --> 01:37.904
=Episode 37=

01:39.568 --> 01:43.984
♪My life is full of ups and downs♪

01:45.744 --> 01:49.904
♪Every wound shows traces of love♪

01:50.896 --> 01:55.952
♪I've seen all the withering plants
in this world♪

01:56.848 --> 01:59.536
♪Until you went over the hills♪

01:59.984 --> 02:02.224
♪To come close to me♪

02:03.824 --> 02:08.240
♪I saw your tender yet unwavering eyes♪

02:10.160 --> 02:14.384
♪Quietly full of joy and sorrow♪

02:15.280 --> 02:21.008
♪When it's over, I stand in the light♪

02:21.424 --> 02:25.968
♪In the reunion,
I comprehend the parting♪

02:27.184 --> 02:32.400
♪With half a lifetime of separation,
I send love to the distance♪

02:33.328 --> 02:39.216
♪As I travel through wind and frost,
I gaze at your figure♪

02:39.376 --> 02:44.688
♪You never forget me,
and I always miss you♪

02:45.712 --> 02:51.452
♪Even with gray hair,
I still look like I was in my youth♪

02:52.464 --> 02:57.360
♪I ask, have you been well♪

03:12.816 --> 03:17.840
♪Unafraid, as time strips away the past♪

03:19.503 --> 03:24.324
♪Revealing the unforgettable textures♪

03:24.432 --> 03:30.224
♪Those regrets fade with the years♪

03:30.672 --> 03:35.888
♪In every dawn and dusk, life endures♪

03:39.632 --> 03:45.106
♪With half a lifetime of separation,
I let love grow wild♪

03:45.919 --> 03:51.131
♪Through the wind and frost,
you come to my side♪

03:51.856 --> 03:53.456
I will definitely come back safely.

03:56.377 --> 03:57.856
Then I wish you

03:58.456 --> 03:59.696
a victorious first battle,

04:00.217 --> 04:01.377
and a swift return home.

04:06.015 --> 04:11.472
♪You say,
there's still a long way ahead♪

04:12.097 --> 04:12.977
Your Highness.

04:13.377 --> 04:14.696
Your Highness, bad news!

04:15.097 --> 04:16.176
Terrible!

04:16.376 --> 04:17.816
The people of the capital

04:17.816 --> 04:19.496
have surrounded Prince Li's Mansion.

04:19.777 --> 04:20.496
What's going on?

04:20.657 --> 04:22.337
News of Prince Li's rebellion
has spread.

04:22.537 --> 04:25.137
The people have been stirred up
by those with ulterior motives,

04:25.137 --> 04:26.416
and gone to Prince Li's Mansion.

04:26.577 --> 04:28.816
I hope Princess Li would be fine.

04:33.736 --> 04:34.657
Who's there?

04:34.897 --> 04:35.697
Your Highness.

04:52.496 --> 04:53.217
Stop.

04:57.856 --> 05:00.816
They say the battles in the north
are related to His Highness.

05:02.296 --> 05:03.577
His Highness is still alive,

05:04.176 --> 05:04.936
isn't he?

05:14.897 --> 05:15.577
Now,

05:16.936 --> 05:18.056
Mo Jingli's rebellion

05:18.856 --> 05:20.017
is known to all.

05:21.616 --> 05:23.256
Prince Li's Mansion is no longer safe.

05:24.657 --> 05:26.864
There must be a battle
between the court and Mo Jingli.

05:27.496 --> 05:30.056
Dachu will fall into chaos.

05:32.097 --> 05:33.376
Then what should I do?

05:34.097 --> 05:35.897
Even if you now announce to the world

05:35.897 --> 05:38.296
that you've parted ways with him
and drawn a clear line,

05:38.657 --> 05:40.256
you will still be at risk.

05:40.936 --> 05:42.856
So you must leave
the capital immediately.

05:43.256 --> 05:45.416
Find a secret place and hide well

05:45.936 --> 05:47.496
until everything settles.

05:53.616 --> 05:54.777
I'll go find him.

05:59.056 --> 06:00.176
Are you insane?

06:01.816 --> 06:02.496
Ye Ying.

06:03.376 --> 06:04.856
I understand you.

06:05.657 --> 06:07.256
But you can't drain yourself dry

06:07.256 --> 06:09.296
trying to light a lamp
you simply can't light.

06:10.256 --> 06:10.897
Ye Li.

06:12.777 --> 06:13.856
I only know

06:15.017 --> 06:16.457
that since His Highness left,

06:16.616 --> 06:18.496
I haven't had
a single good night's sleep.

06:20.577 --> 06:23.056
My heart feels
as if it's been carved out

06:23.616 --> 06:25.017
and placed over a fire to roast.

06:30.376 --> 06:31.537
I just...

06:33.457 --> 06:35.256
just want to see him one more time.

06:42.017 --> 06:43.296
Please, let me go.

06:49.416 --> 06:50.256
Li.

07:07.697 --> 07:09.176
This journey is perilous.

07:11.296 --> 07:12.856
Have you truly made up your mind?

07:16.697 --> 07:17.816
After I leave,

07:18.496 --> 07:19.816
please tell Mom

07:20.777 --> 07:21.816
that I

07:23.977 --> 07:25.416
have gone on a long journey

07:27.616 --> 07:28.537
to clear my mind.

07:34.097 --> 07:34.936
Alright.

08:14.697 --> 08:16.376
Just let these people take her away?

08:17.856 --> 08:20.496
She's made up her mind.
There's no way to stop her.

08:21.056 --> 08:22.337
This battle against Mo Jingli

08:22.777 --> 08:25.176
will ruin the peace at Suixue Pass
and bring chaos to it.

08:25.777 --> 08:27.217
It's truly despicable and hateful.

08:28.577 --> 08:29.897
Any news from Prince Ding?

08:33.016 --> 08:34.697
He has fought against Cangbei for years.

08:34.937 --> 08:36.376
Mo Jingli isn't a real threat yet.

08:36.656 --> 08:37.496
Don't worry.

08:37.656 --> 08:38.697
Prince Ding will be fine.

08:43.057 --> 08:44.177
He promised me

08:45.457 --> 08:46.896
he would return safely.

09:28.656 --> 09:29.337
Your Highness,

09:29.457 --> 09:30.616
don't stand here in the wind.

09:30.776 --> 09:32.736
It's getting cold.
Careful not to catch a chill.

09:33.457 --> 09:34.536
By this hour,

09:35.057 --> 09:37.177
Ye Ying should have crossed
the Qingzhou border.

09:38.577 --> 09:39.896
The front line is perilous.

09:39.896 --> 09:41.736
Is Princess Li truly
going to Luoxia Pass

09:41.736 --> 09:42.937
to seek Prince Li?

09:45.136 --> 09:46.817
Will she be able to see Prince Ding?

10:07.136 --> 10:07.937
Your Highness.

10:12.496 --> 10:15.408
(We escorted Princess Li
out of the capital days ago.)

10:15.408 --> 10:16.752
(The front line is perilous.)

10:16.752 --> 10:18.097
(For Princess Li's safety,)

10:18.097 --> 10:20.736
(we have now settled her
at a residence in Qingshi Township.)

10:20.736 --> 10:22.320
(We hereby report to Your Highness.)

10:40.464 --> 10:41.168
And here.

10:45.376 --> 10:47.057
Has Mo Xiuyao arrived with his troops?

10:47.977 --> 10:48.656
Yes.

10:49.057 --> 10:50.217
The emperor has appointed him

10:50.217 --> 10:52.016
as Commander of Northern Border Campaign

10:52.016 --> 10:53.177
to quell the rebellion.

10:53.177 --> 10:56.016
He is now inside Luoxia Pass.

10:57.896 --> 10:59.057
Perfect timing.

11:03.736 --> 11:06.776
Leading the elite troops of Suixue Pass,
Mo Jingli captured three cities.

11:06.776 --> 11:09.177
He's been recruiting soldiers
and incorporating bandits.

11:09.896 --> 11:11.376
When he reached Heishui River,

11:12.136 --> 11:13.376
he had over 80,000 soldiers,

11:13.376 --> 11:14.417
with strong momentum.

11:15.097 --> 11:15.937
General Deng,

11:16.337 --> 11:17.337
how are our forces?

11:17.376 --> 11:19.097
Including
the garrison forces in the pass

11:19.097 --> 11:21.776
and the hastily conscripted militia,
we have under 30,000 soldiers.

11:21.776 --> 11:23.937
That's less than
half the enemy's strength.

11:23.977 --> 11:24.776
Reinforcements?

11:25.337 --> 11:26.217
Still on the way,

11:26.417 --> 11:27.977
but they need more time to arrive.

11:33.008 --> 11:34.337
Carts and horses can't pass here.

11:34.337 --> 11:34.977
It's defensible.

11:35.337 --> 11:36.136
This area

11:36.337 --> 11:38.577
has a narrow pass,
easy to defend and hard to attack.

11:38.856 --> 11:40.136
Dispatch soldiers to defend it.

11:40.896 --> 11:42.896
This is the supply transport route.

11:43.097 --> 11:44.736
We must ensure its absolute safety.

11:46.136 --> 11:47.496
Luoxia Pass must not be captured.

11:48.136 --> 11:49.057
Once it got captured,

11:49.536 --> 11:51.616
behind it lies
a thousand miles of flat plains,

11:51.896 --> 11:53.016
with no defensible terrain.

11:54.256 --> 11:56.697
The rebels could
reach the capital within ten days.

11:59.097 --> 12:00.136
The survival of our nation

12:00.656 --> 12:01.616
rests on all of you.

12:02.016 --> 12:02.817
We must

12:03.616 --> 12:04.616
win this battle.

12:04.896 --> 12:06.736
- We'll defend the pass with our lives!
- We'll defend the pass with our lives!

12:12.937 --> 12:14.896
You've been transferred
to the Imperial Court.

12:15.097 --> 12:17.496
Why did you volunteer
to endure this hardship with me?

12:18.736 --> 12:21.136
Behind Luoxia Pass is my home.

12:26.097 --> 12:28.616
I remember it.
Xiaoshui County in Lingzhou.

12:30.457 --> 12:31.856
We will protect it well.

12:35.217 --> 12:36.337
Come on, guests.

12:36.337 --> 12:37.417
Want to check this?

12:37.417 --> 12:38.417
Of course.

12:39.417 --> 12:40.177
Senior.

12:46.376 --> 12:47.376
That's it.

12:47.776 --> 12:49.217
I searched everywhere but failed.

12:49.496 --> 12:50.297
I never thought

12:50.776 --> 12:52.016
I truly left it here.

12:52.577 --> 12:53.776
Our staff picked it up.

12:53.896 --> 12:55.376
I knew at a glance it was yours.

12:55.577 --> 12:58.136
I thought to send someone
to deliver it to you after closing.

12:58.937 --> 12:59.937
I happened to be

13:00.016 --> 13:02.016
on my way to work,
so it saves you trouble.

13:04.856 --> 13:05.376
How is it?

13:05.376 --> 13:06.097
Recently,

13:06.736 --> 13:08.177
how has business been at the shop?

13:10.577 --> 13:11.616
You saw it for yourself.

13:12.337 --> 13:15.016
There are few people in the shop
and few on the streets.

13:15.297 --> 13:16.784
The staff outnumber the customers.

13:18.016 --> 13:18.937
The war is deadlocked.

13:20.016 --> 13:21.217
So, people are unsettled.

13:23.376 --> 13:24.097
Has His Highness

13:24.736 --> 13:26.177
sent any letters home?

13:28.376 --> 13:29.656
Not for half a month.

13:32.977 --> 13:35.136
I heard some whispers
at the Ministry of Revenue.

13:36.097 --> 13:37.896
Minister Cui has been frowning lately,

13:38.337 --> 13:40.376
saying the supplies
at front line are running low,

13:40.417 --> 13:41.736
requiring the urgent transport.

13:46.057 --> 13:46.817
Li.

13:48.177 --> 13:49.016
Rest assured.

13:49.457 --> 13:51.440
His Highness
is a master of military strategy.

13:51.536 --> 13:52.776
He'll defeat the enemy safely.

13:54.136 --> 13:55.136
Of course.

13:59.056 --> 14:01.616
Prince Ding joined the army young
and fought hundreds of battles.

14:01.616 --> 14:03.016
Despite the peril at Suixue Pass,

14:03.016 --> 14:04.177
he still turned the tide.

14:04.697 --> 14:07.496
The current situation is far less dire,
so he'll surely win.

14:09.177 --> 14:11.097
Steward Tang, you are wrong.

14:11.297 --> 14:12.097
First,

14:12.136 --> 14:14.496
Luoxia Pass is not
a formidable fortress.

14:14.656 --> 14:15.937
It lacks terrain advantage.

14:16.697 --> 14:19.337
Last year's droughts and floods
disrupted the transport canals,

14:19.896 --> 14:21.856
making the supplies transport difficult.

14:22.417 --> 14:23.177
Second,

14:23.376 --> 14:25.817
Prince Li's forces
are skilled frontier troops,

14:26.136 --> 14:27.536
but our forces are not the same.

14:27.736 --> 14:29.177
We accept the battle in haste.

14:29.297 --> 14:31.792
We are inferior in
both numbers and experience.

14:32.697 --> 14:34.217
- In my opinion...
- In my opinion,

14:34.217 --> 14:36.337
heaven protects Dachu.
Our army will surely win!

14:37.256 --> 14:39.616
Stop it. Don't you see
whose shop this is?

14:44.817 --> 14:45.776
Make way!

14:46.448 --> 14:47.044
Hyah!

14:47.817 --> 14:48.577
Make way!

14:48.977 --> 14:50.177
Report from Luoxia Pass!

14:54.977 --> 14:56.016
Where is Duke Hua?

14:58.776 --> 14:59.776
Your Majesty,

15:00.496 --> 15:03.417
Duke Hua is gravely ill
and has taken leave to recuperate.

15:06.376 --> 15:08.016
We lost the first battle at Luoxia Pass.

15:08.016 --> 15:09.136
What are your thoughts?

15:09.337 --> 15:10.136
Your Majesty,

15:10.536 --> 15:11.417
in my opinion,

15:11.736 --> 15:13.496
victory and defeat
are both common in battle.

15:13.496 --> 15:15.417
Though the rebels won temporarily,

15:15.776 --> 15:18.457
our reinforcements
from the southwest and southeast

15:18.457 --> 15:20.016
are already on their way to assist.

15:20.337 --> 15:22.697
Once Prince Ding
consolidates the forces,

15:22.697 --> 15:25.097
he will surely wipe out
the rebels in one swift move.

15:25.577 --> 15:26.376
Your Majesty,

15:26.937 --> 15:27.817
as the saying goes,

15:27.896 --> 15:29.616
"Think first of defeat,
then of victory."

15:30.097 --> 15:31.177
In my opinion,

15:31.736 --> 15:34.376
several units must be exhausted
from long-distance marches.

15:34.376 --> 15:36.097
They should not
go directly to Luoxia Pass.

15:36.496 --> 15:38.417
They should establish
a second line of defense

15:38.417 --> 15:41.097
behind it at Shuangtuo Ridge
and prepare for battles.

15:41.097 --> 15:42.776
If Luoxia Pass falls,

15:42.776 --> 15:44.624
we can still halt the enemy,

15:44.937 --> 15:46.297
and protect the capital region.

15:46.656 --> 15:48.776
Our front-line forces
are fighting outnumbered.

15:49.177 --> 15:51.097
It's common for the outcome
to be unpredictable.

15:52.016 --> 15:54.417
Shuangtuo Ridge in the rear
holds high ground,

15:54.616 --> 15:57.177
but just thirty li to its west
lies flat plains.

15:57.337 --> 15:58.977
If the rebels take a detour,

15:59.977 --> 16:01.536
there will be no defensible terrain.

16:02.016 --> 16:04.376
In that case, just divide our forces
to defend strictly.

16:04.656 --> 16:05.977
Dividing our forces to defend?

16:06.057 --> 16:06.776
Absurd!

16:06.776 --> 16:08.616
Dividing our forces can't defend at all.

16:09.457 --> 16:10.297
It is truly

16:10.616 --> 16:12.337
a waste of manpower.

16:13.697 --> 16:16.080
You are merely a Vice Director
of the Ministry of Revenue.

16:16.080 --> 16:16.817
What do you know?

16:17.256 --> 16:18.697
How dare you question me?

16:19.376 --> 16:21.177
I am not familiar
with battle formations,

16:21.977 --> 16:24.297
but I do know
a little about calculation.

16:24.536 --> 16:27.817
There are seven paths of varying sizes
around Shuangtuo Ridge.

16:27.937 --> 16:30.417
If we divide our forces,
our military strength will be divided.

16:30.457 --> 16:33.496
Then what about supplies,
transport, and consumption?

16:33.977 --> 16:36.616
Reinforcements not going to the front,
but retreating to the rear.

16:36.736 --> 16:38.817
May I ask how many books
on the art of war you read?

16:38.817 --> 16:39.817
You!

16:39.937 --> 16:40.697
Enough!

16:42.656 --> 16:43.616
What do you think?

16:45.616 --> 16:46.417
Your Majesty,

16:46.977 --> 16:47.817
in my opinion,

16:47.856 --> 16:49.736
victory or defeat
is a matter of the moment.

16:50.337 --> 16:52.417
The court should remain steady.

16:52.536 --> 16:54.097
Front line might suffer minor setbacks.

16:54.136 --> 16:56.536
And we must be even more stable.

16:57.097 --> 16:59.016
If we panic and lose our composure,

16:59.417 --> 17:02.136
it will only cause more trouble.

17:02.457 --> 17:03.256
Your Majesty.

17:04.857 --> 17:06.377
I make bold to petition.

17:06.377 --> 17:07.776
Be cautious about internal threats.

17:08.400 --> 17:11.440
The collapse of a great edifice
often begins with rot in its beams.

17:11.440 --> 17:12.752
Your Majesty.

17:23.736 --> 17:25.016
All those ministers in court

17:25.056 --> 17:26.217
get paid from the government,

17:26.617 --> 17:29.496
yet at this critical moment,
none can relieve my worries.

17:29.576 --> 17:31.496
They are all just empty talkers!

17:33.776 --> 17:34.617
Minister Murong,

17:34.857 --> 17:35.897
what is your view?

17:38.296 --> 17:39.417
Calm down, Your Majesty.

17:39.776 --> 17:42.776
They are all loyal and concerned
for the nation, hence the debate.

17:43.377 --> 17:45.137
However, this matter is too significant.

17:45.536 --> 17:47.657
It still requires
Your Majesty's decision.

17:47.657 --> 17:48.496
Gongshu Yang,

17:48.736 --> 17:49.576
speak.

17:49.736 --> 17:50.536
Your Majesty,

17:50.736 --> 17:52.417
may I speak frankly?

17:52.897 --> 17:53.736
Go ahead.

17:54.897 --> 17:56.296
As you command.

17:58.296 --> 18:00.617
Most of the ministers
aren't well-versed in military,

18:00.617 --> 18:02.736
but they are all well-read.

18:02.736 --> 18:04.897
There are military strategies
passed down in the books.

18:05.576 --> 18:06.816
For a simple fact

18:06.816 --> 18:08.296
that dividing forces now isn't wise,

18:08.336 --> 18:10.296
I bet everyone knows.

18:11.177 --> 18:12.217
In my opinion,

18:12.457 --> 18:14.768
what they're worried about is

18:15.377 --> 18:17.776
that they fear Prince Ding
might rebel with troops in hand.

18:18.296 --> 18:19.217
Eight years ago,

18:19.296 --> 18:22.296
Prince Ding's brother, Mo Xiuwen,
came back to rescue the late emperor,

18:22.296 --> 18:23.776
yet met such a tragic end.

18:24.576 --> 18:25.536
Now,

18:25.736 --> 18:27.776
the battle at Luoxia Pass
is at a stalemate.

18:27.937 --> 18:29.377
No one can be certain

18:29.496 --> 18:32.496
that Prince Ding
is absolutely loyal to you.

18:32.697 --> 18:33.496
But

18:33.897 --> 18:36.177
what the ministers think doesn't matter.

18:36.457 --> 18:37.417
What matters

18:37.736 --> 18:39.536
is what you think.

18:40.816 --> 18:42.217
You had him quell the rebels,

18:42.336 --> 18:44.096
yet feared he might
use the troops to rebel.

18:44.096 --> 18:45.496
You feared he might

18:45.496 --> 18:47.096
collude with Mo Jingli like Li Duo.

18:47.096 --> 18:49.496
You feared Dachu would
collapse in an instant.

18:49.496 --> 18:50.256
How dare you!

18:54.457 --> 18:55.897
I deserve death.

18:56.016 --> 18:57.617
Calm down, Your Majesty.

19:09.336 --> 19:10.296
Your Majesty,

19:10.536 --> 19:12.137
the Empress Dowager has returned.

19:42.776 --> 19:43.576
Mother.

19:48.336 --> 19:49.736
Is everything okay?

19:50.296 --> 19:51.137
You look

19:51.336 --> 19:52.496
quite fine.

19:53.256 --> 19:54.296
I am fine.

19:54.937 --> 19:56.897
Has your health improved, Mother?

19:57.137 --> 19:58.816
Enjoy the life at the temporary palace?

19:59.776 --> 20:01.336
That place is serene and refined.

20:01.457 --> 20:03.177
I am also well in every way.

20:05.857 --> 20:07.776
Mother, you suddenly returned.

20:08.457 --> 20:10.177
Is it because you heard
about the battle?

20:14.736 --> 20:17.336
I returned for these orchids.

20:18.016 --> 20:20.377
I have been tending them
since I entered the palace.

20:21.177 --> 20:23.697
Repotting them at spring,
warming them in the room in winter.

20:23.736 --> 20:25.177
I've never entrusted them to others.

20:25.897 --> 20:27.217
I feared

20:27.457 --> 20:30.352
the bumpy journey would damage them,
so I didn't bring them along.

20:30.617 --> 20:32.937
I entrusted two reliable maids
to care for them.

20:33.424 --> 20:34.776
But while I was away,

20:35.056 --> 20:36.816
I feared
they wouldn't be well cared for.

20:37.177 --> 20:38.897
Unable to rest easy, so I came back.

20:40.417 --> 20:42.177
But I was overthinking.

20:42.977 --> 20:44.177
They are well cared for.

20:46.377 --> 20:47.776
Mother, if you returned

20:48.296 --> 20:49.937
and saw these flowers already withered,

20:50.336 --> 20:52.417
would you regret
entrusting them to others?

20:55.457 --> 20:56.256
No.

20:57.336 --> 20:59.177
Because at the moment of entrusting,

20:59.576 --> 21:01.697
I had already made the best choice.

21:02.457 --> 21:03.296
Besides,

21:03.937 --> 21:05.617
as long as the roots are not withered,

21:06.336 --> 21:09.137
there is always a way
to turn things around.

21:09.617 --> 21:11.736
You should only use those you trust.

21:12.056 --> 21:13.177
It's a basic principle.

21:17.096 --> 21:18.377
Thank you for your guidance.

21:33.296 --> 21:35.496
Mother, are you no longer angry with me?

21:38.177 --> 21:40.937
In my youth, I always thought

21:41.016 --> 21:42.417
there was only one path to take.

21:43.256 --> 21:44.897
I pushed aside those blocking me.

21:45.177 --> 21:46.496
I eliminated those against me.

21:47.256 --> 21:49.177
After situations changed,

21:50.617 --> 21:52.457
I only realized that what's done

21:53.977 --> 21:55.937
is done, and can't be undone.

21:56.617 --> 21:58.496
I was also like this when I was young.

21:59.457 --> 22:01.217
I thought some paths must be taken

22:01.457 --> 22:02.697
and fought for.

22:03.056 --> 22:04.937
But looking back, I can't even tell

22:05.256 --> 22:06.496
whether it was worth it or not.

22:08.016 --> 22:09.016
I made a mess.

22:09.897 --> 22:11.177
So, did you come back

22:11.217 --> 22:12.816
to clean up the mess for me?

22:16.816 --> 22:17.937
I came back

22:18.776 --> 22:20.056
because I missed you.

22:25.977 --> 22:28.736
Duke, this is your first time
at Anqing Palace, right?

22:30.857 --> 22:33.177
I am old and frail,

22:34.056 --> 22:36.336
and can no longer serve the country.

22:37.496 --> 22:40.377
Why would I trouble Your Majesty?

22:41.937 --> 22:43.617
So, Duke, why are you

22:43.977 --> 22:44.977
coming today?

22:48.816 --> 22:49.617
Everyone, leave.

22:59.177 --> 23:00.617
To me,

23:01.576 --> 23:03.816
there's one thing

23:04.536 --> 23:06.377
I can't let go of.

23:10.217 --> 23:14.137
Forty-six people at Lishan Academy

23:16.056 --> 23:18.576
perished from an illness.

23:21.177 --> 23:22.336
I know

23:23.056 --> 23:25.417
you and Master Qingyun
were close friends.

23:25.897 --> 23:26.736
The court

23:26.977 --> 23:28.657
has compensated the bereaved families

23:28.657 --> 23:29.816
and rebuilt the academy,

23:30.096 --> 23:31.217
to comfort the departed.

23:32.776 --> 23:33.617
Duke,

23:33.937 --> 23:35.137
you must restrain your grief.

23:36.736 --> 23:39.977
But I recently learned

23:41.897 --> 23:46.377
that Lishan Mountain was besieged
by troops for eight whole years,

23:47.377 --> 23:49.377
lacking food and medicine.

23:50.457 --> 23:53.296
Lishan Mountain
was full of talented people,

23:54.617 --> 23:58.617
and even had a renowned physician
like Master Helai.

23:58.897 --> 24:01.496
How could an acute illness

24:01.496 --> 24:02.937
cause such calamity?

24:03.816 --> 24:05.496
I want to know,

24:07.016 --> 24:08.217
was Lishan Mountain's tragedy

24:08.697 --> 24:10.776
truly a natural disaster entirely

24:11.697 --> 24:14.256
with no human intervention?

24:15.457 --> 24:17.360
I did send troops back then,

24:18.016 --> 24:19.776
but had no intention of besieging.

24:20.457 --> 24:22.377
Then what do you mean?

24:26.377 --> 24:27.857
Qingyun

24:28.417 --> 24:31.576
blocked your path to the throne.

24:33.336 --> 24:35.177
Didn't you hate him?

24:35.457 --> 24:38.217
It was Lu Changfu
who besieged Lishan Mountain.

24:38.697 --> 24:42.056
Did you truly not know
what he was doing?

24:44.816 --> 24:46.697
So, Duke, you're here today

24:46.977 --> 24:48.736
to pin this groundless accusation

24:48.736 --> 24:50.336
on me?

24:52.736 --> 24:54.032
Lishan Mountain was besieged,

24:54.256 --> 24:55.336
lacking food and medicine.

24:55.857 --> 24:57.576
I only learned about it today as well.

24:57.937 --> 24:58.857
Moreover,

24:59.096 --> 25:00.937
the one who went to Lishan
eight years ago

25:00.977 --> 25:03.336
was you, not me.

25:11.457 --> 25:12.256
Indeed.

25:13.096 --> 25:13.897
Indeed.

25:15.576 --> 25:18.977
It was I who begged Qingyun
to seal itself off back then,

25:20.296 --> 25:21.177
only to

25:21.697 --> 25:24.177
thwart your ambition to the throne.

25:30.657 --> 25:31.977
In that case,

25:33.016 --> 25:34.288
are you

25:34.960 --> 25:36.056
feeling guilty,

25:36.137 --> 25:37.177
unable to sleep at night,

25:37.937 --> 25:40.096
so seeking a scapegoat

25:40.576 --> 25:43.096
to place your own remorse?

25:45.904 --> 25:46.640
Yes.

25:48.336 --> 25:50.736
I failed Qingyun.

25:52.657 --> 25:53.457
I let him

25:54.016 --> 25:56.576
and the entire Lishan bear it all.

25:57.697 --> 25:59.137
For the rest of my life,

25:59.736 --> 26:01.457
I will find it hard to be at peace.

26:01.736 --> 26:02.576
However,

26:03.897 --> 26:05.256
lately,

26:05.417 --> 26:06.937
I cannot help but recall

26:08.816 --> 26:10.576
the great fire at the Eastern Palace,

26:11.617 --> 26:13.256
the lost decree,

26:14.417 --> 26:16.256
and the sealing of Lishan.

26:16.536 --> 26:17.857
Whether all of these

26:18.256 --> 26:22.736
were truly tribulations
of the nation's fate,

26:23.496 --> 26:24.336
or

26:24.736 --> 26:27.937
the schemes on your path to power.

26:28.977 --> 26:30.096
In these matters,

26:30.496 --> 26:32.457
are you truly

26:33.137 --> 26:35.336
completely innocent?

26:38.192 --> 26:40.576
The Hua family has served
the nation for three generations.

26:40.576 --> 26:42.177
I have always held it in high regard.

26:43.256 --> 26:45.177
But don't think that this
gives you the right

26:45.657 --> 26:47.576
to pin this fabricated accusation on me.

26:54.697 --> 26:58.296
I am 71 years old this year,

26:59.177 --> 27:00.977
sick, disabled, and frail.

27:02.417 --> 27:04.536
What else is there to fear?

27:05.857 --> 27:08.096
I only seek the truth.

27:10.177 --> 27:11.897
Whether you believe it or not,

27:12.336 --> 27:13.536
the Lishan Mountain matter

27:13.776 --> 27:15.296
truly has nothing to do with me.

27:28.816 --> 27:30.657
Since you are unwell,

27:31.256 --> 27:32.096
from now on,

27:32.417 --> 27:34.296
you should rest easy
and recuperate at home.

27:35.096 --> 27:36.296
You don't need

27:37.056 --> 27:38.336
to worry about court affairs.

27:38.336 --> 27:39.457
You!

27:55.096 --> 27:55.937
Duke.

27:58.736 --> 27:59.857
Do you

28:00.217 --> 28:01.536
wish to die here,

28:02.296 --> 28:03.576
just to confirm

28:04.137 --> 28:06.697
the slander
that I persecute loyal ministers?

28:07.736 --> 28:08.697
Your Majesty.

28:10.496 --> 28:13.256
The will of Heaven cannot be disobeyed.

28:14.177 --> 28:16.857
The will of the people
cannot be disobeyed.

28:18.496 --> 28:19.986
Your own conscience

28:21.296 --> 28:23.697
cannot be disobeyed.

28:25.897 --> 28:27.376
I just

28:27.920 --> 28:29.496
hope,

28:30.897 --> 28:34.336
when you meet the late emperor

28:35.096 --> 28:36.416
and those who died unjustly

28:36.416 --> 28:38.736
in the netherworld in the future,

28:39.697 --> 28:42.657
you can also be at peace.

28:46.897 --> 28:48.657
(I was also like this when I was young.)

28:49.857 --> 28:51.496
I thought some paths must be taken

28:51.697 --> 28:52.816
and fought for.

28:53.137 --> 28:55.016
But looking back, I can't even tell

28:55.296 --> 28:56.536
whether it was worth it or not.

29:34.536 --> 29:36.056
- Careful, Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

29:43.457 --> 29:44.296
Your Highness.

29:44.296 --> 29:46.137
Please come down. You might fall.

29:46.137 --> 29:47.417
Be careful, Your Highness.

29:48.496 --> 29:49.217
Your Highness.

29:49.217 --> 29:50.897
The baby bird's mother is back.

29:51.336 --> 29:52.857
Come down, Your Highness.

29:53.617 --> 29:54.536
Be careful.

29:55.177 --> 29:56.377
Don't peck me.

29:56.977 --> 29:58.776
Your child fell down.

29:58.776 --> 30:00.377
I am just sending it home.

30:06.832 --> 30:07.632
- Be careful.
- Li.

30:07.760 --> 30:09.336
- Ms. Wen.
- What are you doing up there?

30:10.056 --> 30:11.977
- A baby bird fell down.
- Careful!

30:11.977 --> 30:13.056
I'm sending it back.

30:13.296 --> 30:14.137
Be careful.

30:15.816 --> 30:16.496
Come on.

30:18.217 --> 30:20.336
You didn't have to go up yourself.

30:20.336 --> 30:21.336
Are you okay?

30:21.617 --> 30:22.536
I'm fine.

30:22.536 --> 30:23.697
I enjoy the exercise.

30:23.816 --> 30:24.617
Your Highness.

30:24.736 --> 30:25.536
Ms. Wen.

30:26.377 --> 30:27.056
Your Highness.

30:28.736 --> 30:29.417
Your Highness.

30:29.417 --> 30:30.217
Ms. Wen.

30:30.256 --> 30:31.857
A letter from the frontier has arrived.

30:39.377 --> 30:40.177
I just heard

30:40.336 --> 30:41.336
about a major defeat.

30:41.336 --> 30:41.977
What?

30:41.977 --> 30:43.137
Has Luoxia Pass fallen?

30:43.137 --> 30:43.736
No.

30:43.736 --> 30:44.536
Really?

30:45.016 --> 30:45.697
Tell me more.

30:45.697 --> 30:46.657
How is Luoxia Pass?

30:46.977 --> 30:47.816
It hasn't fallen.

30:47.816 --> 30:49.096
But over 20,000 people died.

30:49.536 --> 30:50.776
So many corpses and blood.

30:50.776 --> 30:51.776
Over 20,000 people died?

30:51.776 --> 30:53.056
Doesn't that mean it's fallen?

30:53.816 --> 30:54.736
Not that many.

30:54.736 --> 30:55.536
Only 2,000 killed.

30:55.536 --> 30:57.137
I heard the enemy lost even more.

30:57.177 --> 30:59.016
But I heard earlier

30:59.016 --> 31:00.657
that Prince Ding
has sided with Prince Li.

31:00.657 --> 31:01.336
When?

31:01.336 --> 31:02.336
Prince Ding defected?

31:02.576 --> 31:04.096
I heard that too. It's everywhere.

31:04.096 --> 31:05.296
- It's true.
- He defected?

31:05.336 --> 31:06.512
Prince Ding defected.

31:07.016 --> 31:08.377
Prince Li is coming.

31:09.496 --> 31:10.336
Hurry!

31:12.096 --> 31:13.617
What's going on?

31:14.937 --> 31:16.256
I'm relieved now.

31:18.256 --> 31:19.056
Wuyou.

31:19.217 --> 31:20.977
Why didn't you go to school today?

31:23.177 --> 31:25.177
The teacher said
it's been unsettled lately,

31:25.377 --> 31:26.776
and told me to stay home.

31:29.697 --> 31:30.496
That's fine.

31:30.977 --> 31:32.857
If you don't go, I will teach you.

31:34.457 --> 31:35.256
Come.

31:35.377 --> 31:36.857
Xi, go prepare some tea.

31:36.857 --> 31:37.657
Yes.

31:42.897 --> 31:43.617
Your Highness.

31:43.617 --> 31:44.417
Ms. Wen.

31:44.857 --> 31:46.096
Go head. What's the matter?

31:46.977 --> 31:48.576
Rumors are spreading wildly outside.

31:48.576 --> 31:50.217
Some say Luoxia Pass has fallen,

31:50.217 --> 31:51.417
and others say

31:52.296 --> 31:53.576
that His Highness defected.

31:54.617 --> 31:55.697
Nonsense!

31:55.937 --> 31:57.657
Xiuyao's letter clearly stated

31:57.697 --> 31:59.296
that the front line faces minor defeats,

31:59.296 --> 32:00.536
but both sides are tied.

32:00.536 --> 32:01.897
How dare they spread rumors!

32:03.536 --> 32:04.657
Are the rumors widespread?

32:04.816 --> 32:05.657
Your Highness.

32:05.657 --> 32:06.377
Yes.

32:06.657 --> 32:08.096
People are all talking about it.

32:08.096 --> 32:09.937
It's causing widespread panic.

32:12.536 --> 32:14.417
Go to Jingzhao Prefecture
and find Gu Zheng.

32:14.617 --> 32:16.697
Have him investigate
the source of these rumors.

32:17.336 --> 32:18.457
Such rumors

32:18.897 --> 32:20.336
would never be spread from nowhere.

32:20.496 --> 32:23.016
I bet someone
is deliberately stirring up trouble.

32:23.977 --> 32:24.776
Yes.

32:29.576 --> 32:30.377
Li.

32:31.657 --> 32:32.457
Ms. Wen.

32:33.056 --> 32:34.016
Everything will be fine.

32:46.816 --> 32:47.617
Your Majesty.

32:48.496 --> 32:49.336
You

32:49.657 --> 32:51.536
should at least eat something.

32:51.816 --> 32:52.897
Perhaps His Majesty

32:53.417 --> 32:55.016
has been delayed by state affairs.

32:58.457 --> 33:00.112
With the war at a stalemate,

33:00.417 --> 33:01.840
military reports are piling up.

33:02.256 --> 33:04.336
His Majesty is surely
too busy to get away.

33:06.736 --> 33:07.897
He won't come.

33:08.217 --> 33:09.697
Please don't think that way.

33:09.697 --> 33:10.697
He will come.

33:10.897 --> 33:12.697
You've raised His Majesty
since his childhood.

33:12.897 --> 33:13.897
Deep mother-son bond.

33:15.736 --> 33:16.617
Perhaps

33:17.096 --> 33:18.496
he was burdened by various thoughts

33:18.736 --> 33:20.080
and couldn't figure out for now.

33:20.296 --> 33:21.657
After His Majesty thinks it over,

33:21.697 --> 33:24.096
he'll understand your efforts
to protect him all along.

33:25.897 --> 33:26.736
Really?

33:27.137 --> 33:28.736
Of course, it's true.

33:29.496 --> 33:31.336
Nothing can beat

33:31.336 --> 33:32.937
the mother-son bond.

33:34.857 --> 33:35.657
Besides,

33:36.217 --> 33:38.056
there was an urgent report this morning.

33:38.657 --> 33:39.736
Rumors spread

33:40.016 --> 33:41.496
that Prince Ding suffered defeats.

33:41.496 --> 33:42.897
He might have defected.

33:42.937 --> 33:43.937
Now, His Majesty

33:43.937 --> 33:45.417
might be

33:45.496 --> 33:46.897
worrying about this matter.

33:49.256 --> 33:50.056
Indeed.

33:50.617 --> 33:51.897
We are mother and son.

33:52.697 --> 33:54.617
He is my only child.

33:55.336 --> 33:56.496
That is exactly the point.

33:56.697 --> 33:58.096
His Majesty just began his reign.

33:58.177 --> 33:59.336
He still needs your advice

33:59.417 --> 34:01.536
on many important matters.

34:02.857 --> 34:04.016
Yanqi is kind-hearted

34:04.217 --> 34:05.617
and inexperienced.

34:06.256 --> 34:08.616
I need to support him more.

34:10.496 --> 34:12.417
Now, whether Prince Ding

34:12.457 --> 34:14.737
harbors resentment to the court
is still a question.

34:15.937 --> 34:16.696
This time,

34:16.937 --> 34:18.656
he holds military power again.

34:19.136 --> 34:21.216
We must remain vigilant.

34:31.337 --> 34:32.937
Deliver a portion of Golden Milk Pastry

34:33.056 --> 34:34.257
to Prince Ding's Mansion

34:35.337 --> 34:36.696
and invite Princess Ding to come.

34:37.337 --> 34:38.136
I wish

34:38.937 --> 34:40.337
to enjoy the flowers with her.

34:43.656 --> 34:44.457
Yes.

34:44.696 --> 34:45.696
I'll go handle it.

34:59.496 --> 35:00.297
Your Highness.

35:03.897 --> 35:05.496
This is bestowed by Her Majesty.

35:21.297 --> 35:22.257
Look at you,

35:22.377 --> 35:24.016
you seem to have lost some weight.

35:24.696 --> 35:26.616
Are the household affairs troubling you?

35:27.616 --> 35:28.897
Thank you for your concern.

35:29.857 --> 35:31.016
Recently,

35:31.176 --> 35:33.656
I have had trouble sleeping
due to missing His Highness.

35:34.016 --> 35:35.417
Sorry to worry you.

35:36.377 --> 35:38.000
Prince Ding is fighting at the frontier.

35:38.192 --> 35:40.457
Managing the household alone
is no easy task.

35:44.457 --> 35:45.817
Look at these chrysanthemums.

35:46.457 --> 35:47.696
They bloom in the frost,

35:48.297 --> 35:50.937
yet still cannot withstand
the power of changing seasons.

35:53.016 --> 35:54.176
All things in the world

35:55.096 --> 35:56.977
must follow the natural order.

35:59.096 --> 36:01.096
It's getting cold lately.

36:03.176 --> 36:04.297
Take care of yourself.

36:05.576 --> 36:07.977
I will keep your kind advice in mind.

36:09.897 --> 36:12.297
We've received
many battle reports from the frontier.

36:12.977 --> 36:14.696
The situation seems unfavorable.

36:16.656 --> 36:18.576
Prince Ding leading the troops far away

36:19.016 --> 36:21.576
must be having a difficult time.

36:22.297 --> 36:23.176
Your Majesty.

36:23.777 --> 36:25.496
Being able to serve the court

36:25.656 --> 36:26.817
is his duty.

36:27.257 --> 36:29.777
With Your Majesty and His Majesty
commanding the court,

36:29.857 --> 36:32.176
I am confident
that he could turn danger into safety.

36:32.696 --> 36:33.817
Prince Ding is valiant.

36:34.096 --> 36:36.297
I also have confidence in him.

36:37.897 --> 36:39.457
However, in the court,

36:39.616 --> 36:41.696
there are inevitably
some ignorant people

36:41.857 --> 36:42.977
trying to stir up trouble.

36:43.576 --> 36:44.696
I heard

36:45.297 --> 36:47.337
that some people are questioning

36:47.337 --> 36:49.096
Prince Ding's military strategy.

36:50.056 --> 36:51.297
How absurd!

36:54.096 --> 36:55.216
The art of warfare

36:55.777 --> 36:58.937
lies in the right timing,
advantage of terrain, and unity of men.

36:59.496 --> 37:00.857
Temporary gains and losses

37:01.216 --> 37:02.817
may not determine the final outcome.

37:03.696 --> 37:04.817
You are so kind,

37:04.977 --> 37:06.576
shielding His Highness in every way.

37:06.897 --> 37:09.096
I also believe in His Highness.

37:10.496 --> 37:12.817
It is best that you think this way.

37:13.457 --> 37:14.496
However, in recent days,

37:14.656 --> 37:16.457
you should leave the mansion less often,

37:17.016 --> 37:18.897
to avoid hearing improper words,

37:19.216 --> 37:20.297
which might annoy you.

37:23.136 --> 37:23.937
I heard

37:24.297 --> 37:25.817
rumors circulate among the people.

37:27.857 --> 37:28.696
Yes.

37:30.496 --> 37:31.377
Sit down.

37:36.937 --> 37:38.136
Why don't you

37:38.176 --> 37:40.417
stay in the palace for a few days?

37:41.257 --> 37:44.096
First, it can spare you the loneliness
of staying in the chamber alone.

37:44.737 --> 37:45.536
Second,

37:45.576 --> 37:47.696
you can avoid those ignorant people.

37:48.817 --> 37:50.417
When Prince Ding returns in triumph,

37:50.857 --> 37:52.977
he can see you safe and sound.

37:55.817 --> 37:57.576
I am willing to stay in the palace

37:57.576 --> 37:59.016
to heed Your Majesty's teachings.

37:59.496 --> 38:01.216
It could also ease His Highness's mind

38:01.216 --> 38:02.297
during his campaign.

38:12.457 --> 38:13.457
Her Majesty said

38:13.457 --> 38:15.656
you could settle in here
with peace of mind.

38:15.696 --> 38:17.777
If you need anything,
just tell the palace maids.

38:18.297 --> 38:19.457
Thank you, Senior Eunuch.

38:20.457 --> 38:22.096
Your Highness, don't mention it.

38:23.016 --> 38:25.297
Serve Princess Ding well.
Let there be no mistake.

38:26.297 --> 38:27.096
- Yes.
- Yes.

38:28.656 --> 38:30.096
If you have no further instructions,

38:30.257 --> 38:31.817
I shall take my leave first.

38:48.777 --> 38:50.377
Please prepare some tea
for Her Highness.

38:51.297 --> 38:52.096
- Yes.
- Yes.

39:06.937 --> 39:07.777
(Yao.)

39:08.576 --> 39:09.576
(Hope you're doing well.)

39:10.800 --> 39:12.616
(I have been
in the Empress Dowager's palace)

39:12.616 --> 39:14.096
(for a while now.)

39:15.016 --> 39:16.616
(Early autumn has arrived recently.)

39:17.216 --> 39:19.216
(Thin frost covers the steps
early morning.)

39:20.337 --> 39:21.536
(I often lean by the window,)

39:22.096 --> 39:24.297
(watching the small patch of sky
framed by the window.)

39:25.536 --> 39:27.016
(Clouds occasionally drift by.)

39:27.417 --> 39:28.417
(They come hastily,)

39:29.016 --> 39:30.337
(and then go hastily,)

39:30.777 --> 39:32.257
(never staying for anyone.)

39:33.817 --> 39:35.257
(The days in the palace are long.)

39:36.096 --> 39:37.857
(Occasionally,
I play a game of Go alone.)

39:38.377 --> 39:41.337
(On the Go board, I lose track of time.)

39:42.536 --> 39:44.576
(However, the rules on the Go board)

39:44.576 --> 39:46.216
(are sometimes puzzling.)

39:47.496 --> 39:49.817
(A move that is clearly meant
to expand and explore)

39:50.176 --> 39:53.136
(is often criticized by onlookers
for being too sharp)

39:53.857 --> 39:55.216
(and easily inviting disaster.)

39:55.777 --> 39:57.297
(Better to retreat for safety.)

39:58.777 --> 40:00.016
(A chess piece has no will.)

40:00.377 --> 40:01.536
(Where it'll be put)

40:02.096 --> 40:03.656
(is entirely up to the player.)

40:05.096 --> 40:05.897
(Yao.)

40:06.536 --> 40:07.696
(If you were here,)

40:08.377 --> 40:10.937
(you would surely understand
the meaning behind these moves.)

40:13.016 --> 40:14.417
(Two days ago, I received new tea.)

40:14.737 --> 40:16.336
(Sweet in taste yet cold by nature.)

40:16.937 --> 40:18.992
(After drinking,
I often wake up in the late night.)

40:19.656 --> 40:21.520
(Suddenly, I heard
wild geese's cries outside.)

40:22.056 --> 40:23.136
(Sounded urgent,)

40:23.737 --> 40:24.937
(as if urging a return home.)

40:26.337 --> 40:28.144
(I recalled the bitter cold
at the frontier.)

40:28.457 --> 40:30.897
(By now, the north wind
must be howling fiercely.)

40:32.216 --> 40:33.817
(I hope you take good care of yourself)

40:34.576 --> 40:35.857
(and keep warm.)

40:38.216 --> 40:39.600
(Moonlight is like a silk ribbon.)

40:39.817 --> 40:41.056
(I send my longing from afar,)

40:42.696 --> 40:44.297
(wishing the moonlight shines upon you.)

40:45.656 --> 40:46.937
(A letter from your wife,)

40:47.777 --> 40:48.417
(Li.)

40:57.937 --> 40:58.737
Your Highness.

40:59.496 --> 41:02.257
You've been reading
this two-page letter for two hours.

41:02.696 --> 41:04.176
Is there some hidden meaning

41:04.817 --> 41:05.857
in Her Highness's letter?

41:08.457 --> 41:10.096
Her Majesty summoned Li to the palace,

41:10.096 --> 41:12.696
saying to keep her company,
but actually to hold her hostage.

41:14.016 --> 41:16.496
It seems someone in the palace
fears my military power

41:17.457 --> 41:18.257
and suspects

41:18.777 --> 41:20.457
that I have colluded with Mo Jingli.

41:23.088 --> 41:24.496
So they are holding her hostage

41:24.777 --> 41:25.977
to restrain me.

41:30.297 --> 41:32.817
Any report on the enemy's encampment?

41:34.297 --> 41:35.656
As you predicted,

41:35.656 --> 41:37.417
they gather
on the west side of Jueyun Brook.

41:38.377 --> 41:39.176
Previously,

41:39.257 --> 41:41.016
Mo Jingli's camp was fortified
with terrain.

41:41.297 --> 41:42.576
His command tent
was hidden deep,

41:42.576 --> 41:44.656
and the supply camp was
high up and heavily guarded.

41:44.656 --> 41:46.096
But after our army feigned defeat,

41:46.817 --> 41:47.897
abandoned the eastern pass,

41:48.297 --> 41:49.297
and pretended to retreat

41:49.297 --> 41:51.016
from Duanhun Slope and Suishi Valley,

41:51.817 --> 41:52.977
the enemy grows bolder.

41:53.616 --> 41:54.897
They're expanding their camp

41:55.337 --> 41:56.897
and relaxing their outer defenses.

41:57.536 --> 41:58.337
Yesterday,

41:58.417 --> 42:00.616
Mo Jingli even moved
his command tent three li forward.

42:00.817 --> 42:02.857
For the convenience of fetching water,

42:02.897 --> 42:04.977
they moved the supply camp
to a lower canyon area.

42:05.176 --> 42:06.257
Now it seems

42:06.576 --> 42:08.457
that they believe
our forces have collapsed,

42:08.696 --> 42:09.457
and want

42:10.096 --> 42:11.257
to strike Luoxia Pass.

42:11.696 --> 42:12.977
Arrogance courts defeat.

42:13.977 --> 42:15.656
Order the army to be ready for battle.

42:16.897 --> 42:17.696
This battle

42:18.536 --> 42:19.824
must be settled swiftly.

42:20.696 --> 42:21.496
Yes.

42:43.568 --> 42:46.224
(Preview)

42:47.016 --> 42:48.897
Prince Ding set an ambush
at Jueyun Brook,

42:48.977 --> 42:50.737
wiping out Mo Jingli's main rebel force.

42:50.977 --> 42:52.400
The leader Mo Jingli's on the run.

42:52.400 --> 42:53.857
They are currently pursuing him.

42:54.056 --> 42:55.472
The people of Lishan Mountain

42:55.857 --> 42:57.257
did die of an acute illness.

42:57.656 --> 42:58.817
Lacking food and medicine

42:59.257 --> 43:00.176
is undeniable.

43:00.377 --> 43:01.777
Are you blaming me?

43:02.136 --> 43:03.496
Merits and faults are clear.

43:03.977 --> 43:05.096
The justice in this world

43:05.616 --> 43:07.937
is never as simple as
offsetting one with the other.

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
♪Unbound by form♪
